item.title: DELL
item.description: score:37 Chances: Dell Technologies (DELL) is at a 52-week high, but can investors hope for more gains in the future? We take a look at the company’s fundamentals for clues. The stock has outperformed Apple over the past five years. What will the next five years look like?
